  "text": "VAESum [CITATION_1] employs an alignment mechanism [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] to recall the lost detailed information from the input sentence. Inspired this idea, we design a jointly weighted alignment mechanism by considering the news sentence and the comment sentence simultaneously. For each decoder hidden state s i h , we align it with each news encoder hidden state h j d",
